## Post-restart default-model drift

The verifier caught a post-restart app default drift:

- defaults read run.pentagon.app pentagon.defaultModel: claude-opus-4-7[1m]

Corrected it back to the required default:

- defaults write run.pentagon.app pentagon.defaultModel gpt-5.5
- defaults read run.pentagon.app pentagon.defaultModel: gpt-5.5
- audit-pentagon-native-poller-surface default_model: gpt-5.5

Live active_graph agent rows remained aligned as codex|gpt-5.5|codex|local.

