## Verdict

The native activation blocker is no longer absolute after restarting Pentagon.app. A corrected 90-second native-only probe passed with no bridge attribution. The full goal remains open because this proves native activation smoke, not yet repo-specific easy, medium, hard, and extra-hard native task execution.
